acquireTime.Description: MicroTime is version of Time with microsecond level precision.

holderIdentity.Description: holderIdentity contains the identity of the holder of a current lease.

leaseDurationSeconds.Description: leaseDurationSeconds is a duration that candidates for a lease need to wait to force acquire it. This is measure against time of last observed RenewTime.

leaseTransitions.Description: leaseTransitions is the number of transitions of a lease between holders.

renewTime.Description: MicroTime is version of Time with microsecond level precision.

spec.Description: LeaseSpec is a specification of a Lease.
